#

Quick Weeknight Borscht

45 min
$10
180 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Eastern European

Course:

Main

Tags:

SoupQuickHearty

Description

A vibrant beet soup that's both hearty and refreshing, perfect for a quick weeknight dinner.

Ingredients

  • beets: 3 medium, peeled and grated
  • cabbage: 2 cups, shredded
  • carrots: 1 large, grated
  • potato: 1 large, diced
  • vegetable broth: 4 cups
  • dill: 1 tablespoon, chopped (for garnish)
  • sour cream: ½ cup (for serving)
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
